{"title":"[图论]最小圈","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1115#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=1115","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1115/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1115/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/1115"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给出一个有向图，求这个图的路径长度平均值最小的环。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行包含两个整数n和m,并用一个空格隔开，其中n=|V|,m=|E|分别表示图中有n个点和m条边。接下来是m行，每行包含用空格隔开的3个数i,j和W(i,j),表示一条边（i,j）且该边的权值W（i,j）。输入数据保证图G（V，E）连通，存在圈且有一个点能到达其它所有点。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅包含一个实数∮（C）=MIN{∮(C)},要求输出到小数点后8位。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入样例1：\r\n```\r\n2 2\r\n1 2 -2.9\r\n2 1 -3.1\r\n```\r\n输出样例1：\r\n```\r\n-3.00000000 \r\n```\r\n输入样例2：\r\n```\r\n4 5\r\n1 2 5\r\n2 3 5\r\n3 1 5\r\n2 4 3\r\n4 1 3\r\n```\r\n输出样例2：\r\n```\r\n3.66666667 \r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"20%的数据：n<=100.m<=1000;\r\n50%的数据：n<=1000.m<=5000;\r\n100%的数据：n<=3000.m<=10000;\r\n1000%的数据：|W(i,j)|<=10^7."}]}